overview: Dr. Mark Jewell is a member of the American Board of Plastic Surgery and is currently the United States National Secretary for the International Society for Aesthetic Plastic Surgery. He served as President of the American Society for Aesthetic Plastic Surgery (ASAPS), as a Governor for the National Endowment for Plastic Surgery and as a member of the American Association of Plastic Surgeons. Dr. Jewell has published over 60 peer-reviewed scientific papers, books, and book chapters. He is a respected educator who has lectured and performed surgery to teach other plastic surgeons within the US and Europe, South America, Asia, the Mid-East, and Australia.
